#: addon\appModules\line.py:2998
msgid ""
"圖片描述功能會將目前訊息的螢幕截圖上傳至雲端 AI 服務 {provider} 進行辨識。\n"
"是否同意？選「是」之後，使用這項服務時不會再詢問。\n"
"可在「NVDA 功能表 → 偏好設定 → 設定 → LINE Desktop」更換服務或設定自己的 API 金鑰；更換服務後會再次詢問。"
msgstr ""
"The image description feature uploads a screenshot of the current message to the cloud AI service {provider}.\n"
"Do you agree? After choosing Yes you will not be asked again for this service.\n"
"You can change the service or set your own API key under NVDA menu → Preferences → Settings → LINE Desktop; changing the service asks again."

